Third-party components and data (their licenses apply):

- js-aruco2 (https://github.com/damianofalcioni/js-aruco2) â€” ArUco detection in the browser.
- AprilTag detection: script loaded from arenaxr.github.io/apriltag-js-standalone (WASM); see that project for license.
- ArUco dictionaries: OpenCV-style DICT_4X4 (50, 250, 1000 codes); byte-swap option for OpenCV compatibility.
- AprilTag 36h11: 587 codes, same layout as the official 36h11 family (AprilRobotics); used for generation and display only; detection uses the standalone WASM build above.
